<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-05-21T12:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-05-21T12:00:00-05:00" n="367" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d367">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 841.731/1769</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Ambassador in Great Britain</hi> (<persName corresp="frus1917Supp02v01#p_PWH1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Page</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-05-21T12:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">May 21, 1917, 12 noon</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>4856. Your 6059, April 21, 6 p.m. Re-establishment British censorship
                            desirable. Please so inform British Government and request they
                            designate representative, if practicable a member of the commission now
                            here, to confer with United States chief cable censor with a view to
                            uniformity of regulations, efficiency of operation and exchange of
                            information.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="frus1917Supp02v01#p_LR1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>